                     <note type="general">Written along the fibers; the back is blank</note>
                     <note type="general">18 lines of writing by a medium-sized hand, written quickly</note>
                     <note type="general">Dated on the basis of other papyri relating to Claudia Isidora, a well-known landowner of considerable wealth</note>
